                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6277" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0968</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8397 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南极电商：“品牌授权”造就业界黑马</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">NanJi E-Commerce Co.,LTD: &quot;Brand authorization&quot; creates a dark horse in the field of e-commerce</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">方慧，沈月姿</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海大学MBA教育管理中心</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南极电商股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南极电商；品牌授权；财务状况 ；盈利能力；财务风险</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> NanJi E-Commerce Co.,LTD ； brand authorization ；   financial situation ；profitability ；financial risk</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021年1月初，南极电商因遭到“财务造假”质疑，股价连续暴跌，直到12日，股价已从年初13.61元下跌至9.06元，市值跌破300亿元。南极电商使劲浑身解数，从紧急发布澄清公告到股份回购，希望能重塑企业形象，恢复投资者信心，但南极电商的股价一直都在高低起伏中动荡不停。2021年1月15日，证监会将南极电商纳入重点监控范围。本文对南极电商的发展历程、业务领域及财务状况进行介绍分析，引导学生了解企业财务报表粉饰的预警信号，通过南极电商案例引导学生学习如何对品牌授权这类特殊商业模式企业的财务状况和盈利能力展开分析，并思考和讨论如何对品牌授权类商业模式企业的财务风险进行识别和监管。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">At the beginning of January 2021, the stock price of NanJi E-Commerce Co.,LTD plummeted continuously due to the question of &quot;financial fraud&quot;. Until the 12th, the stock price had fallen from 13.61 yuan at the beginning of the year to 906 yuan, and the market value had fallen below 30 billion yuan. NanJi E-Commerce Co.,LTD has tried its best, from emergency Clarification Announcement to share repurchase, hoping to reshape the corporate image and restore investor confidence, but the stock price of NanJi E-Commerce Co.,LTD has been volatile in ups and downs. On January 15, 2021, NanJi E-Commerce Co.,LTD was included in the key monitoring scope by the CSRC. This paper introduces and analyzes the development process, business fields and financial situation of NanJi E-Commerce Co.,LTD, guides students to understand the early warning signals of corporate financial statement whitewashing, and guides students to learn how to analyze the financial situation and profitability of enterprises with special business models such as brand authorization through the case of NanJi E-Commerce Co.,LTD, It also considers and discusses how to identify and supervise the financial risks of brand authorized business model enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务报表分析》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">股权质押；大股东减持；营业收入与成本；毛利率与净利率；经营性现金流品牌授权；应收账款周转率；总资产周转率；资产负债率；GMV；盈利能力指标关联关系；价值评估</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-05</td>
